cu.explanation_en: Setting gNB_name to an invalid string 'invalid_name' will cause gNB identification errors during initialization.

du.explanation_en: Setting gNB_name to an invalid string 'invalid_name' will cause gNB identification errors during initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB_name 設定為無效字串 'invalid_name' 會在初始化期間導致 gNB 識別錯誤。
